Prerequirements for Installation
- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -

 * A running MySQL database (4.1 or greater).
 * A webserver with PHP4 support.


Installation Instructions
- - - - - - - - - - - - - -

- Copy the contents of the "src/" directory to your webserver, including all
  subdirectories.

- Edit the file "config.inc.php" according to your needs. It should be self
  explaining.

- Create your database tables using the file mysql_matpath.sql. If you have a
  rented webspace, you usually do this by loading the file in the phpMyAdmin
  tool provided by your webspace provider.

- Done. You can now open the webpage.

Do not hesitate to contact me if you run into problems installing the
software. Also, do not forget to file bugs on the homepage if you find any.
